Package: PathwayVolcano
Type: Package
Title: Pathway-Specific Volcano Plots for Differential Expression Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "O'Connell", email = "thoconne@iu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application that integrates the 'Reactome' API 
    to generate pathway-specific volcano plots for differential expression results. 
    Designed to support visual analysis and exploration of pathway-level 'omics' data such as 'transcriptomics'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: 
    stringr,
    ggplot2,
    shiny,
    dplyr,
    ReactomeContentService4R
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
